# **08  Risks and mitigations**

| **Risk** | **Likelihood** | **Impact** | **Mitigation** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **Conversion rate below 2% at Day 90** | Medium | High — delays revenue | Extend free period by 30 days. Investigate which premium features drive intent. Add more value before paywall. |
| **Ad revenue too low to sustain free tier** | Medium | Medium — model pressure | Indian CPM is low (₹50–150 per 1,000 impressions). Do not depend on ads — subscription is primary. Ads are supplementary. |
| **Apple App Store commission (30%)** | Certain | High — margin impact | Offer annual subscription (lower monthly effective price) via website / UPI to bypass App Store billing where legal. |
| **Users leave at Day 90 paywall** | Medium | High — retention drop | 90-day habit is strong. Personalised conversion message referencing household history reduces churn. Referral reward reduces price objection. |
| **Premium Plus features insufficient to justify ₹149** | Low | Medium | Launch Premium Plus only when 3+ features are fully built. Never launch with 1 locked feature as the premium differentiation. |

